      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9090/agents/guardian/run-sync",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"input\": {\n    \"prompt\": \"ETHICS / POLICY / VALIDITY check on the TEXT POST below (no video exists yet). The actual content to check is in context.creator_output. Emit VERDICT=APPROVE | VERDICT=REVISE | VERDICT=BLOCK as the first line, then your JSON. On BLOCK call add_banned_pattern; on REVISE send_agent_message to creator.\",\n    \"context\": {\n      \"phase\": \"pre-render-ethics\",\n      \"creator_output\": {{ JSON.stringify($('✍️ Creator (retry — cheap)').isExecuted ? $('✍️ Creator (retry — cheap)').item.json.output : $('✍️ Creator').item.json.output) }},\n      \"reviewer_verdict\": {{ JSON.stringify($json.output) }}\n    }\n  }\n}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 1800000
        }
      },
