    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Credit-aware design\n\n**Cheap gates run FIRST** (text-only, ~$0.10/call):\n  ✍️ Creator → 🔍 Reviewer-text → 🛡️ Guardian-text\n\n**Expensive step runs ONCE per cycle** (no retries on this):\n  🎬 Visual (Kling render + Nano Banana ×6 + Suno) ≈ $3-5\n\n**Retries cost nothing on the Kling side** — text-only Creator retries don't trigger any rendering.\n\n**On any cheap-gate failure** (Reviewer-text REVISE or Guardian REVISE/BLOCK), Visual is NEVER called. The pack stops and emails for manual review. Credits saved.\n\n**Post-render failures are rare** (text already passed) and go straight to email — no automatic re-render.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 600,
        "color": 1
      },
      "id": "sn-header",
      "name": "📌 Credit-aware design",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        40
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Cheap zone — text only\n*Every retry here costs ~$0.10 (Claude calls only)*\n\n✍️ Creator writes\n🔍 Reviewer checks PROJECT_STANDARDS text rules\n🛡️ Guardian checks ethics on TEXT\n\nIf any of these fail → Creator retry (still no rendering)\n→ if retry also fails → manual email\n\nNo Kling / Nano Banana / Suno calls in this zone.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 320,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "sn-cheap",
      "name": "Cheap zone",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1440,
        980
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Inter-agent messaging\n\nWhen Reviewer or Guardian rejects, they call `send_agent_message(to='creator', subject='REVISE', body=...)` — the message is appended to `virtuai/data/agent_messages.jsonl`.\n\nThe Creator's NEXT call automatically reads this inbox via the API server's auto-inject. Creator fixes the specific issues without burning new credits on Visual.\n\nGuardian BLOCKs also write to `virtuai/data/banned_patterns.json` — Research reads this file before brainstorming so blocked patterns are never proposed again.\n\nAnalyzer writes to `virtuai/data/lessons.json` when a post performs strongly — Research and Strategy read this for direction next cycle.",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "sn-messaging",
      "name": "Inter-agent messaging",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        840,
        980
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
