      },
      "name": "🚀 Render + Publish (agent-seeded, sync)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        2640,
        220
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Render + Publish (agent-seeded, SYNC)\n\nAfter the agent gates APPROVE, this hands the AGENTS' chosen topic/angle to\n/n8n/render-publish-sync, which renders (Kling + Nano Banana + Suno) the\n3-piece pack ABOUT that topic and PUBLISHES — reels -> YouTube + Instagram,\nimages -> Instagram. The node BLOCKS (~12 min) and the live post URLs land\nin the '✅ Pack LIVE' node. (No Wait node — it's broken in this n8n build.)",
        "height": 230,
        "width": 430,
        "color": 3
      },
      "name": "Deterministic zone",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        2600,
        -40
      ]
    },
